      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a reliable foundation for someone looking for a budget-friendly option. The engine starts reliably and the car is drivable, though it does show signs of its age with some cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery. There are a few minor mechanical items that will eventually need attention, such as a slow leak in the power steering and some suspension noise over bumps. Overall, it\u2019s a solid choice for a daily commuter or a weekend project for an enthusiast.",
