      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This unit has been curated to the highest standards, exhibiting no signs of wear or mechanical compromise. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, reflects a history of rigorous stewardship. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber. We invite serious inquiries for a private inspection of this exceptional asset.",
      "price": 48500.0,
