      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I've pampered this car since day one, and it still has that brand-new feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection, you've found it! Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
