    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. The S54B32 inline-six is in peak mechanical health, featuring a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and precise throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring zero drivetrain lash. This specimen has received comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, exceeding factory durability standards. The chassis remains taut with no bushing deflection, riding on a perfectly calibrated suspension that delivers the communicative steering and lateral composure synonymous with the M-division. Impeccably preserved and mechanically flawless.",
